The motorized downdraft hood ascends like a silent performance, the LED frame glows like a halo, and the 5” TFT display illuminates with intuitive clarity. GenX technology refines every gesture: precise cooking, gentle sound, effortless transitions.', NULL, 'https://www.smeg.com/binaries/content/gallery/smeg/awards/news_cover_isola_awards26_960x690.jpg/news_cover_isola_awards26_960x690.jpg/brx%3ApostcardDeskLarge', '2026-06-15T10:00:00Z', true, 260);
INSERT INTO public.news (slug, title, title_en, title_hy, excerpt, excerpt_en, excerpt_hy, category, category_en, category_hy, body, body_en, body_hy, image_url, published_at, is_published, sort_order) VALUES ('new-products-at-eurocucina', 'New SMEG products at Eurocucina 2026', 'New SMEG products at Eurocucina 2026', NULL, 'At Eurocucina 2026, SMEG presents new products that combine contemporary design, advanced technology and style for modern kitchens and living spaces.', 'At Eurocucina 2026, SMEG presents new products that combine contemporary design, advanced technology and style for modern kitchens and living spaces.', NULL, 'Events', 'Events', NULL, 'At the Salone del Mobile, within the biennial Eurocucina exhibition, SMEG presents products designed to enhance everyday life, responding to new ways of living that balance dynamism, conviviality and a growing passion for outdoor experiences, fully reflecting SMEG’s DNA where technology and style come together.

New visions for living and design NEW AESTHETIC LINE Musa: a new aesthetic for the modern kitchen Musa, the new collection developed with the BorromeodeSilva studio, features rounded graphics, material geometry, and a striking contrast between glossy and matt finishes. The collection offers a versatile range - including ovens, induction hobs, warming drawers and a built-in microwave oven - designed to integrate seamlessly into any kitchen style.

NEW AESTHETIC LINE Isola: a light and design concept Isola is the collection created in collaboration with Stefano Boeri Interiors, unveiled at Eurocucina 2024. After taking the Design Intelligence Award 2025 and the authoritative iF Design Awards 2026, the collection makes its market debut with a range consisting of induction hobs with integrated hood, which can be combined with a sophisticated system of illuminated rails, as well as hobs for use with suspended hoods.', 'At the Salone del Mobile, within the biennial Eurocucina exhibition, SMEG presents products designed to enhance everyday life, responding to new ways of living that balance dynamism, conviviality and a growing passion for outdoor experiences, fully reflecting SMEG’s DNA where technology and style come together.

New visions for living and design NEW AESTHETIC LINE Musa: a new aesthetic for the modern kitchen Musa, the new collection developed with the BorromeodeSilva studio, features rounded graphics, material geometry, and a striking contrast between glossy and matt finishes. The collection offers a versatile range - including ovens, induction hobs, warming drawers and a built-in microwave oven - designed to integrate seamlessly into any kitchen style.

NEW AESTHETIC LINE Isola: a light and design concept Isola is the collection created in collaboration with Stefano Boeri Interiors, unveiled at Eurocucina 2024. After taking the Design Intelligence Award 2025 and the authoritative iF Design Awards 2026, the collection makes its market debut with a range consisting of induction hobs with integrated hood, which can be combined with a sophisticated system of illuminated rails, as well as hobs for use with suspended hoods.', NULL, 'https://www.smeg.com/binaries/content/gallery/smeg/stories/smeg---salonedelmobile-milano_0009.png/smeg---salonedelmobile-milano_0009.png/brx%3ApostcardDeskLarge', '2026-06-15T10:00:00Z', true, 250);
