SMEG’s 2026 Novelties Smeg returns to Eurocucina with new design projects shaped by stylistic research and creative collaborations. From refined forms to new matt finish, design evolves into a sensory language that engages both sight and touch.', NULL, 'https://www.smeg.com/binaries/content/gallery/smeg/mdw26/milanodesignweek26_news.jpg/milanodesignweek26_news.jpg/brx%3ApostcardDeskLarge', '2026-06-15T10:00:00Z', true, 240);
