INSERT INTO public.news (slug, title, title_en, title_hy, excerpt, excerpt_en, excerpt_hy, category, category_en, category_hy, body, body_en, body_hy, image_url, published_at, is_published, sort_order) VALUES ('smeg-wins-the-good-design-award-2025', 'SMEG wins the Good Design Award 2025', 'SMEG wins the Good Design Award 2025', NULL, 'SMEG appliances awarded the Good Design Award 2025 by the Chicago Athenaeum', 'SMEG appliances awarded the Good Design Award 2025 by the Chicago Athenaeum', NULL, 'Awards', 'Awards', NULL, 'The SMEG electric barbecue and soda maker awarded by the Chicago Athenaeum Museum of Architecture and Design

The Chicago Athenaeum Museum of Architecture and Design, an international benchmark for over 70 years in contemporary design excellence, has awarded the Good Design Award 2025 to the SMEG Electric Barbecue and Soda Maker, recognized for their aesthetic, functionality, iconic identity, and innovative impact.

Made in Italy technology and design for outdoor cooking SMEG Electric Barbecue The SMEG Electric Barbecue redefines outdoor cooking, making it safe, versatile, and a natural part of everyday life.

Awarded the Good Design Award 2025, it combines aesthetics, functionality, and advanced technical solutions for flame-free cooking, perfect even on balconies and terraces. A new benchmark for outdoor conviviality, where design and performance come together seamlessly.

Perfect balance between design and functionality SMEG Soda Maker The SMEG Soda Maker turns the everyday act of preparing sparkling water into an elegant and personalized experience: it works without electricity, featuring a knob that allows you to adjust the level of carbonation to your taste.

Awarded the Good Design Award 2025, it stands out for its aesthetics and materials, including the durable, dishwasher-safe Tritan™ Renew bottle.

A design that combines style, sustainability, and practicality, making every sip a special moment.

Smeg S.p.A - Via Leonardo da Vinci, 4 42016 Guastalla (RE) Italy

