New products, projects and collaborations with partners of excellence bring Smeg to the stage of Eurocucina 2024. An unmissable opportunity to showcase its latest innovations characterised by unmistakable style, excellent quality and state-of-the-art technology.

ISOLA by Smeg and Stefano Boeri Interiors Stefano Boeri Interiors is inspired by the Smeg classics to create soft, unique lines, shaping a collection capable of transcending the barriers of time. A range of induction hobs, with and without an integrated hood, and a high-tech suspended hood system with a revolutionary, elegant and luminous design.', NULL, 'https://www.smeg.com/binaries/content/gallery/smeg/eurocucina2024.jpg/eurocucina2024.jpg/brx%3ApostcardDeskLarge', '2024-06-15T10:00:00Z', true, 130);
INSERT INTO public.news (slug, title, title_en, title_hy, excerpt, excerpt_en, excerpt_hy, category, category_en, category_hy, body, body_en, body_hy, image_url, published_at, is_published, sort_order) VALUES ('smeg-won-the-good-design-award-2023', 'GOOD DESIGN AWARD 2023: SMEG DESIGN EXCELLENCE', 'GOOD DESIGN AWARD 2023: SMEG DESIGN EXCELLENCE', NULL, 'Smeg Small and Major domestic appliances stand out in the Good design award 2023.', 'Smeg Small and Major domestic appliances stand out in the Good design award 2023.', NULL, 'Awards', 'Awards', NULL, 'More than seventy years of design excellence: an ambitious milestone achieved by the Chicago Athenaeum Museum of Architecture and Design, which each year celebrates the design language with the oldest and most prestigious award in the industry, the Good Design Award. Smeg appliances stand out in the 2023 edition thanks to iconic Made in Italy design and the high standards in terms of durability, aesthetics, functionality and sustainability.', 'More than seventy years of design excellence: an ambitious milestone achieved by the Chicago Athenaeum Museum of Architecture and Design, which each year celebrates the design language with the oldest and most prestigious award in the industry, the Good Design Award. Smeg appliances stand out in the 2023 edition thanks to iconic Made in Italy design and the high standards in terms of durability, aesthetics, functionality and sustainability.', NULL, 'https://www.smeg.com/binaries/content/gallery/smeg/awards/2023_gda_visualbox_960x690-all.jpg/2023_gda_visualbox_960x690-all.jpg/brx%3ApostcardDeskLarge', '2023-06-15T10:00:00Z', true, 120);
