"Guastalla Half Marathon", the charity sports event organised by Smeg with the patronage of the Municipality of Guastalla, is now in its fourth edition.

Scroll There are three routes where participants can test themselves:

Sport, sharing and solidarity are the protagonists of the day, which aims to keep the focus on cancer prevention and treatment. For this reason, all proceeds from the day will be donated to local associations involved in patient care, prevention and the promotion of sport among young people.

Participation is free and the event will take place on 10th September 2023 from 8.30 a.m. CET. For the winners of the competitive marathon, Smeg small appliances will also be up for grabs.

