INSERT INTO public.news (slug, title, title_en, title_hy, excerpt, excerpt_en, excerpt_hy, category, category_en, category_hy, body, body_en, body_hy, image_url, published_at, is_published, sort_order) VALUES ('slate-grey-domestic-appliances', 'SLATE GREY SMALL DOMESTIC APPLIANCES', 'SLATE GREY SMALL DOMESTIC APPLIANCES', NULL, 'Discover Smeg slate grey domestic appliances: stand mixer, kettle and toaster to match', 'Discover Smeg slate grey domestic appliances: stand mixer, kettle and toaster to match', NULL, 'Products', 'Products', NULL, 'SLATE GREY FOR A TRENDY KITCHEN Color plays a fundamental role in the kitchen: it can help create a welcoming atmosphere and define the personality of the space. Smeg appliances were born to be the protagonists of the kitchen with their shades, from the most muted like pastel colors to the brightest like red. For those looking for appliances that define a contemporary space, the new shade of small appliances is the ideal solution: slate grey. A neutral and perfectly versatile tone that can blend as easily into a contemporary industrial space as in a traditional kitchen.

Scroll MUST HAVE APPLIANCES To give a new look to the kitchen, why not focus on the collection of small appliances? Not only versatile and functional: they are perfect to be displayed in the kitchen as real objects with an unmistakable design.

The inevitable combination is that of toaster and kettle.

With fast boiling results, an elegant lid and a generous 1.7 liter capacity, a Smeg kettle is your ally to prepare a hot herbal tea to be enjoyed at any time of the day.

Pair it with your toaster for the best breakfast set. The Smeg 2 Slice Toaster offers uniform browning results with 6 levels to choose from. It is also equipped with bagel, reheat and defrost functions.

Scroll DRIP COFFEE MACHINE If you can''t give up starting your day with coffee, Smeg has the solution for your needs. With the Smeg drip coffee machine in the new slate grey color, you can set the dedicated function and wake up with a fresh coffee every morning.

Personalize your coffee based on the intensity of the aroma you prefer, whether it is delicate or intense. The Smeg filter coffee machine has a 1.4-liter capacity that allows you to prepare up to 10 cups of coffee and a keep-warm function that keeps the coffee hot for up to 40 minutes after brewing.

Scroll SLATE GREY STAND MIXER For baking lovers, the Smeg stand mixer in the new slate grey color offers excellent results and is a pleasant piece of furniture for contemporary environments.

In addition to the unmistakable design that distinguishes it, the slate grey mixer is characterized by high performance and numerous functions.

The best features include a soft start function to gently operate the planetary mixer, a large 4.8 liter stainless steel bowl for mixing or kneading compounds from the smoothest to the most compact.', 'SLATE GREY FOR A TRENDY KITCHEN Color plays a fundamental role in the kitchen: it can help create a welcoming atmosphere and define the personality of the space. Smeg appliances were born to be the protagonists of the kitchen with their shades, from the most muted like pastel colors to the brightest like red. For those looking for appliances that define a contemporary space, the new shade of small appliances is the ideal solution: slate grey. A neutral and perfectly versatile tone that can blend as easily into a contemporary industrial space as in a traditional kitchen.

